1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 10=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(Taken Out of Context,
Full of Affection)

4
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:54,790
Many civil officials in the court,

5
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:57,350
as well as the Hanlin scholars
who usually stay neutral,

6
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,790
are all asking me about you.

7
00:00:59,110 --> 00:01:00,510
They want to know who you really are.

8
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:02,150
This is just the beginning.

9
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:05,000
I'm still far from
becoming a national idol.

10
00:01:05,510 --> 00:01:06,920
I need to release a few more poems.

11
00:01:07,510 --> 00:01:08,920
Tower Master, you love making money,

12
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,560
but creating this newspaper to gain fame

13
00:01:10,620 --> 00:01:12,480
surely isn't just
to save your own life, right?

14
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:18,950
You want to know?

15
00:01:19,350 --> 00:01:20,590
Since I've been running around

16
00:01:20,590 --> 00:01:22,320
and working my fingers
to the bone for you,

17
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:23,350
just tell me, please?

18
00:01:24,350 --> 00:01:25,790
Then...

19
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:28,150
Keep selling the Wangshi Chronicle.

20
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,870
The timing isn't right yet.

21
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,530
We still need to lay more groundwork.

22
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:35,760
When the time is ripe,
you will naturally know.

23
00:01:38,950 --> 00:01:39,710
Tower Master.

24
00:01:39,850 --> 00:01:41,710
Our four printing workshops
in the east, south, west, and north

25
00:01:41,710 --> 00:01:43,420
have all been raided
and shut down by the Inspectorate.

26
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:46,230
All the printing blocks
and newspapers have been confiscated.

27
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:48,840
Were they all destroyed?

28
00:01:49,150 --> 00:01:49,560
Yes.

29
00:01:49,820 --> 00:01:50,680
The moment I arrived,

30
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,890
they threw all of those things
into the furnace.

31
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,390
I managed to salvage a few pieces.

32
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,230
With this tool,

33
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:08,030
making thousands of
copies of documents within a day

34
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:08,960
would be as easy.

35
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,250
If this is promoted everywhere,

36
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:16,850
all the poor scholars in the world
can study the way of the sages.

37
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:17,910
Impressive.

38
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:20,560
What's dangerous
is the Wangshi Chronicle.

39
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,590
If its reach expands further,

40
00:02:25,150 --> 00:02:26,630
it will control public opinion

41
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:28,000
and destabilize the state.

42
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,710
Zheng Yuanhe...

43
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:32,360
I am going to destroy him!

44
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,030
Yuanhe.

45
00:02:36,310 --> 00:02:36,850
Tower Master.

46
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:39,710
Send invitations to all civil officials,
refined scholars,

47
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:40,990
talented men,
and beautiful ladies in the capital.

48
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:43,560
Say that I will host a poetry gathering
at the Second Prince's Residence

49
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:44,980
to make friends through our verses.

50
00:02:45,150 --> 00:02:45,960
Alright.

51
00:02:47,470 --> 00:02:49,280
I wanted to take things slow,

52
00:02:49,330 --> 00:02:51,030
but he's forcing me
to blow this wide open.

53
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:53,840
The more the jerk tries to suppress me,

54
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:56,180
the more I will make
the name of the Tower Master

55
00:02:56,190 --> 00:02:57,240
resound through the skies!

56
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,750
(Pan Residence)
Mr. Zhang.

57
00:03:00,750 --> 00:03:01,520
Mother,

58
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,520
Li Qingqing framed me for all of this.

59
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:05,360
You feed and clothe me,

60
00:03:05,390 --> 00:03:07,000
and you accepted me into the residence.

61
00:03:07,150 --> 00:03:09,190
How could I ever hurt you?

62
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:11,360
You still want
to shift the blame to Qingqing?

63
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:13,840
The man who hit me
has already confessed.

64
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,520
You heard him yourself.

65
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:18,030
He is the shopkeeper
of Li Qingqing's store.

66
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,680
He must be putting on a show with her

67
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,910
just to ruin my relationship with you.

68
00:03:24,590 --> 00:03:25,630
That's right, Mother.

69
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,240
You've really wronged her.

70
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,630
She went out
just to help me buy some things.

71
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,430
Running into you was pure coincidence.

72
00:03:31,900 --> 00:03:33,840
Li Qingqing hasn't been
in the residence at all.

73
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,830
That's why she had
the time to plot these schemes.

74
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:36,960
Nonsense!

75
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,470
What kind of person Qingqing is,

76
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:41,750
we know far better than you do.

77
00:03:42,190 --> 00:03:43,800
Open your eyes and look.

78
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:46,470
Ever since this woman
entered the Pan Residence,

79
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:48,560
how much trouble has she caused?

80
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:51,560
She's trying to harm your mother,

81
00:03:51,810 --> 00:03:53,430
yet you're still
defending her like this.

82
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,590
It's a misunderstanding, Father, Mother.

83
00:03:54,590 --> 00:03:56,000
You've really misunderstood her.

84
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,280
Misunderstood what?

85
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,030
Look at the newspaper.

86
00:03:59,430 --> 00:04:00,590
How are the people outside

87
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,590
gossiping about our family right now?

88
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:04,750
Li Qingqing has money.

89
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,750
She paid

90
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,520
the newspaper to slander me.

91
00:04:07,710 --> 00:04:10,150
That only proves she hired that man.

92
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:12,630
What kind of status does
the Tower Master of Wangshi have?

93
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,520
How could she possibly
be bought off by Qingqing

94
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,480
just to publish
our trivial family matters?

95
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,070
You malicious woman,

96
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,870
you don't even know how to lie.

97
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,720
I am being wronged.

98
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,000
Father, Mother,

99
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:24,510
Muyan really did nothing wrong.

100
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:26,680
Let's go.

101
00:04:27,310 --> 00:04:28,600
Just listen to her.

102
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:30,310
One day, the Pan family

103
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:32,600
will be ruined by this woman.

104
00:04:34,390 --> 00:04:35,310
Master...

105
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:37,240
(Zhao Prince's Residence)

106
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:39,360
Last time I read the Tower Master's
"Bring on the Liquor",

107
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,920
it was breathtaking.

108
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:41,720
Indeed.

109
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,510
If we could witness the Tower Master

110
00:04:43,510 --> 00:04:45,460
recite poetry in person today,
it would be wonderful.

111
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,600
I never expected that a commoner like me

112
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,190
could come to
the Second Prince's residence

113
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,750
to recite poetry and drink tea.

114
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,430
It brings honor to my ancestors.

115
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,480
Yes.

116
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,590
I just came to see the Tower Master.

117
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,190
Quiet down.

118
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,790
The Prince and
the Tower Master are here.

119
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:59,040
They're here.

120
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,190
Follow the Tower Master,

121
00:05:02,190 --> 00:05:03,430
and fame and wealth will follow!

122
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:05,360
- Follow the Tower Master,
- Follow the Tower Master,

123
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,920
- and fame and wealth will follow!
- and fame and wealth will follow!

124
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,000
Tower Master,

125
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:09,040
a role model for women.

126
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,750
We are all your loyal fans.

127
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,160
- Tower Master,
- Tower Master,

128
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,390
- a role model for women.
- a role model for women.

129
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:16,000
- We are all your loyal fans.
- We are all your loyal fans.

130
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:18,360
The Tower Master's talent

131
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,950
is an example for
scholars all over the world.

132
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,750
We men have a slogan too.

133
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:24,390
- Tower Master,
- Tower Master,

134
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:25,990
- your talent spans past and present!
- your talent spans past and present!

135
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,620
- The literary star shines on the tower,
- The literary star shines on the tower,

136
00:05:27,630 --> 00:05:29,420
- blessing all of Great Yong!
- blessing all of Great Yong!

137
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,240
(I expected this,)

138
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:34,000
(but this is just too exaggerated.)

139
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,310
For today's poetry gathering,

140
00:05:35,310 --> 00:05:36,480
you may all converse freely.

141
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,240
When the Tower Master is free,

142
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,560
she can offer
some guidance on your works.

143
00:05:42,510 --> 00:05:43,720
Coming here today was worth it.

144
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:45,560
The Crown Prince arrives!

145
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,430
The Crown Prince...

146
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:48,720
The Crown Prince is here.

147
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,920
(This scheming fool
burned down my printing workshop.)

148
00:05:58,100 --> 00:05:59,560
(Now I have to look over my shoulder)

149
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,040
(just to print a newspaper.)

150
00:06:01,390 --> 00:06:03,160
(What is he up to coming here today?)

151
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,920
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

152
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:09,950
Brother,

153
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,720
coming to my residence today,

154
00:06:11,730 --> 00:06:12,990
is there something I can help you with?

155
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,720
Aren't you hosting
a poetry gathering here?

156
00:06:17,410 --> 00:06:18,830
I simply wanted to come take a look.

157
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:20,870
Unless, Yuanzhao,

158
00:06:21,270 --> 00:06:22,240
you don't welcome me?

159
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:27,040
The Crown Prince
is the finest scholar in Great Yong.

160
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:29,750
Second Prince,
could it be that you're afraid

161
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:31,360
the Crown Prince
will steal your spotlight?

162
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:33,920
Brother,

163
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,000
not at all.

164
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,360
The Tower Master and I
are deeply grateful

165
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:39,830
that you would come
support my poetry gathering.

166
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:52,920
My colleagues and I have admired

167
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,780
the poem "Bring on the Liquor"
for a long time.

168
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:57,000
Tower Master,
may I ask if you're interested

169
00:06:57,010 --> 00:06:58,160
in sharing a new work today?

170
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,750
Writing poetry requires
the right mood and inspiration.

171
00:07:01,750 --> 00:07:03,150
How can one just compose them on a whim?

172
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:05,830
Besides, the Tower Master's
talent is unparalleled.

173
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,240
I'm afraid getting a new poem
from her won't be easy.

174
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,560
I beg to differ.

175
00:07:14,950 --> 00:07:16,920
What do you mean by that, Your Highness?

176
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:19,600
Since "Bring on the Liquor",

177
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,330
the Tower Master
hasn't produced any new work.

178
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:23,330
If she doesn't produce
another masterpiece soon,

179
00:07:23,340 --> 00:07:24,920
I'm afraid scholars across the world

180
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,920
will think she
has run out of inspiration.

181
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,760
They might even think

182
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,190
that her previous poem

183
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,040
was actually
plagiarized from someone else.

184
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,190
What?

185
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:41,040
(He really did
come here to cause trouble.)

186
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,510
The Tower Master's poetry

187
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:44,160
may be world-famous,

188
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:47,270
but no one has ever seen her
compose a poem with their own eyes.

189
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,920
Our Tower Master is second to none.

190
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,480
We all support you.

191
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:53,800
Yes, exactly. We all support you.

192
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,120
Words alone prove nothing.

193
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:58,390
This newspaper is run
by your Wangshi Tower,

194
00:07:58,510 --> 00:07:59,680
and the featured poems

195
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:01,160
belong to Wangshi Tower as well.

196
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,310
How can anyone call that fair?

197
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:10,270
What do you propose then?

198
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,800
A poetry competition.

199
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:15,680
If your Wangshi Tower can best
all the scholars under heaven,

200
00:08:16,310 --> 00:08:18,120
we will accept it.

201
00:08:18,510 --> 00:08:19,800
But if you lose,

202
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:22,510
it proves that Wangshi Tower
operates in the shadows,

203
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,870
ruining the cultural heritage
of Great Yong.

204
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:25,830
It should be permanently banned

205
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:27,020
and forbidden from publishing.

206
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:31,600
Crown Prince, since you
brought people here to challenge us,

207
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,910
I have no reason to refuse.

208
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,390
Why don't you

209
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:38,030
enlighten us first, Crown Prince?

210
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:40,150
(Tower Master is sharp.)

211
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:42,790
(Trying to drag me into this.)

212
00:08:43,750 --> 00:08:44,720
(What a pity.)

213
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:46,000
If you don't dare to,

214
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,390
you can call for reinforcements.

215
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:53,390
His Highness
is the top disciple of the Chancellor.

216
00:08:53,390 --> 00:08:55,030
With His Highness
taking action personally,

217
00:08:55,030 --> 00:08:57,320
every scholar
in Great Yong will be convinced.

218
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,120
Indeed.

219
00:08:58,510 --> 00:09:00,000
His Highness could read at one,

220
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,150
recite poetry at three.

221
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:02,840
He is a rare genius.

222
00:09:03,310 --> 00:09:05,800
Today, His Highness competing in poetry
with the Tower Master

223
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,360
is thrilling.

224
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,840
Two masters clashing,

225
00:09:08,860 --> 00:09:10,360
we are all so blessed to witness this!

226
00:09:10,510 --> 00:09:12,440
Yes, it's going to
be a feast for the eyes.

227
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:13,910
Wonderful.

228
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,000
You're that incredible?

229
00:09:17,510 --> 00:09:18,320
Please.

230
00:09:21,870 --> 00:09:22,720
I see

231
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,960
the winter scenery today is wonderful,

232
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,890
so I will use this as the theme
to compose a poem.

233
00:09:28,670 --> 00:09:29,960
I welcome your critique.

234
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:32,360
We are all ears.

235
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,750
Quick, write it down.

236
00:09:37,510 --> 00:09:38,120
Your Highness.

237
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:51,240
Remnant snow clings
to the plum blossom shadows.

238
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:56,200
The cold wind brushes
against graying hair.

239
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,240
This is...

240
00:09:58,510 --> 00:10:00,910
Leaning on the railing,
gazing at distant peaks.

241
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:06,200
A lonely moon
shines on the day of return.

242
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:10,750
What a fine poem.

243
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:11,600
Indeed.

244
00:10:12,670 --> 00:10:13,320
Splendid.

245
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:14,720
This five-character quatrain

246
00:10:14,870 --> 00:10:16,630
uses remnant snow, plum shadows,

247
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,890
a lonely moon,
and a cold night as the scenery.

248
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:21,390
The wording is exquisite,

249
00:10:21,390 --> 00:10:23,320
blending the scene
and emotion perfectly.

250
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,630
It hides the feeling of longing

251
00:10:25,870 --> 00:10:28,120
within a quiet and solitary realm.

252
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:31,790
It is both subtle and profound.

253
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:33,910
Wonderful.

254
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,630
Brilliant.

255
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:37,910
Of course.

256
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,390
His Highness's literary talent

257
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,630
is unmatched in the world.

258
00:10:41,110 --> 00:10:42,750
The Crown Prince's
five-character quatrain

259
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:44,180
has a profound artistic conception.

260
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:48,000
Just to spark better ideas.

261
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:49,840
Tower Master,

262
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,390
please.

263
00:10:54,270 --> 00:10:56,840
These words are ornate but lack soul.

264
00:10:58,630 --> 00:11:00,960
It is written just like a rigid brick.

265
00:11:05,310 --> 00:11:06,390
All hail the Tower Master!

266
00:11:06,390 --> 00:11:09,350
- All hail the Tower Master!
- All hail the Tower Master!

267
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,710
- All hail the Tower Master!
- All hail the Tower Master!

268
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,990
- Hail the Master!
- Hail the Master!

269
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:15,670
To ensure fairness,

270
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:17,840
since His Highness's poem

271
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:19,960
was inspired by taking in the scenery,

272
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:22,320
surely your poem

273
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:24,960
should also approach it from this angle,
Tower Master.

274
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:28,150
What you mean is,

275
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:29,510
you're afraid I'll cheat?

276
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,240
Fine.

277
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:40,120
I will also write a poem
about winter scenery.

278
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:53,700
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

279
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:57,860
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

280
00:11:58,620 --> 00:12:00,380
♪Your smile♪

281
00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:02,900
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

282
00:12:02,900 --> 00:12:06,580
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

283
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:10,380
♪Yet I stand before you♪

284
00:12:11,100 --> 00:12:14,940
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

285
00:12:15,340 --> 00:12:17,260
♪Though fate tries♪

286
00:12:17,260 --> 00:12:19,860
♪To make us pass each other by♪

287
00:12:20,060 --> 00:12:23,500
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

288
00:12:23,740 --> 00:12:25,380
♪Though time slips by♪

289
00:12:25,380 --> 00:12:27,140
♪As day turns into night♪

290
00:12:27,660 --> 00:12:31,700
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

291
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:34,500
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

292
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:36,260
♪Blessed by fate♪

293
00:12:36,260 --> 00:12:41,420
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

294
00:12:41,420 --> 00:12:43,860
♪Your smiling face♪

295
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:46,700
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

296
00:12:46,700 --> 00:12:50,340
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

297
00:12:50,860 --> 00:12:54,300
♪And wander the world together♪

298
00:12:54,300 --> 00:12:55,660
♪Holding you close♪

299
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:58,180
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

300
00:12:58,180 --> 00:13:00,500
♪Your tenderness♪

301
00:13:00,500 --> 00:13:03,380
♪Is the brightest moon♪

302
00:13:03,380 --> 00:13:07,060
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

303
00:13:07,580 --> 00:13:10,900
♪Our love will never fade away♪

304
00:13:10,900 --> 00:13:13,340
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

305
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:18,140
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

